snippet.title: PipeMaster B10L - BASIC10Liner game for Commodore 264 series (16,Plus4,116,232) by FeCO
snippet.description:
This is the 10-line version of my previous PipeMaster titles, Extrem256 category.
Just connect the pipe ends with the elements displayed on the center of the screen or left on the field. You cannot move across the dark box. You can rotate the objects, but beware the time limit bar (left side). If you are ready press 'R'. If you completed the field bonus points will added. It time is up, the field will be flooded.
Try yourself in 20 different fields - or play with your friend in two player mode. Enjoy the game!
